105
00:06:18.833 --> 00:06:20.750
My goodness. What's the matter?

106
00:06:21.250 --> 00:06:23.250
Oh. my princess.

107
00:06:23.333 --> 00:06:25.125
What's the matter?

108
00:06:25.208 --> 00:06:27.583
Huh? Oh. Hello.

109
00:06:27.666 --> 00:06:30.833
-Hello. hello.
-Just stop it. Stop it.

110
00:06:30.916 --> 00:06:32.166
-Stop it.
-Baby. what's wrong?

111
00:06:32.250 --> 00:06:34.083
Please go put them in a vase.

112
00:06:34.166 --> 00:06:37.458
A vase? Forget the vase.
because I want you. What vase?

113
00:06:38.166 --> 00:06:41.666
Didn't you say Joyce is throwing you
a massive party? What are you doing here?

114
00:06:41.750 --> 00:06:44.125
Listen. you and I just got married.

115
00:06:44.208 --> 00:06:46.875
