-Calm the baby down.

125
00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:09.291
I'll just put the tip.

126
00:07:09.791 --> 00:07:11.000
Ah. my goodness.

127
00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:12.541
Oh. Jane.

128
00:07:12.625 --> 00:07:15.541
-Ah. greetings. Mr. Gomora.
-Oh. thank goodness. Please take her.

129
00:07:15.625 --> 00:07:17.416
-Please take her. take her.
-There we go.

130
00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:19.833
-I need to rush somewhere.
-Sorry. my girl.

131
00:07:19.916 --> 00:07:21.833
What are they doing to you? Hmm?

132
00:07:21.916 --> 00:07:23.750
-Let me get out of here.
-Huh?

133
00:07:25.666 --> 00:07:28.458
Here.

134
00:07:29.708 --> 00:07:32.041
To me and you.

135
00:07:34.666 --> 00:07:37.041
You smell amazing.

136
00:07:37.125 --> 00:07:38.416
Hold on.

137
00:07:39.125 --> 00:07:40.666
Hold on. there's a car outside.

138
00:07:40.750 --> 00:07:42.000
-Hold on a minute.
-Okay.

139
00:07:43.458 --> 00:07:44.666
