-What?

142
00:07:50.416 --> 00:07:51.666
That's my husband!

143
00:07:53.041 --> 00:07:54.291
You're married. Essie?

144
00:07:55.541 --> 00:07:56.541
Where is everyone?

145
00:07:56.625 --> 00:07:58.083
Oh?

146
00:07:58.166 --> 00:07:59.625
So. you're here.

147
00:07:59.708 --> 00:08:02.916
Are my eyes deceiving me right now?

148
00:08:03.458 --> 00:08:04.541
What's wrong?

149
00:08:04.625 --> 00:08:06.041
It's really him.

150
00:08:06.583 --> 00:08:07.583
-Hey--
-Dad!

151
00:08:07.666 --> 00:08:08.875
Hey. boy! Hey. boy!

152
00:08:08.958 --> 00:08:09.916
Ah. no. Dad.

153
00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:11.583
Are you high?
You've been drinking. haven't you?

154
00:08:11.666 --> 00:08:13.833
He's going to kill you
if he finds you here.

155
00:08:13.916 --> 00:08:15.500
-Go. go. go. go.
-Where am I supposed to go. Essie?

156
00:08:15.583 --> 00:08:16.666
Make a plan.

157
00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:18.083
It's been a while.

158
00:08:18.166 --> 00:08:22.458
You know. my mother.
she has a surprise upstairs for you!

159
00:08:22.541 --> 00:08:23.583
Surprise?

160
00:08:23.666 --> 00:08:25.375
-Get out. Leave. leave.
-Essie.

161
00:08:25.458 --> 00:08:26.666
Get out. I'll call you.

162
00:08:28.125 --> 00:08:30.500
-Mm-hmm.
-And what surprise is that?

163
00:08:30.583 --> 00:08:32.875
-Let's go upstairs--
-Oh. Gomora.

164
00:08:32.958 --> 00:08:35.333
Out of the way.

165
00:08:35.416 --> 00:08:36.416
-Wow.
-Hello.

166
00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:38.458
-What are you doing here?
-What am I doing here?

167
00:08:39.083 --> 00:08:40.500
You complain when I'm here.

168
00:08:40.583 --> 00:08:42.333
You complain when I'm not here.

169
00:08:42.416 --> 00:08:43.416
Uh. I'm not complaining.

170
00:08:43.500 --> 00:08:45.041
Wow.

171
00:08:45.125 --> 00:08:47.791
-You're not complaining?
-Stop it.

172
00:08:47.875 --> 00:08:50.541
Uh. what I'm trying to say. uh.

173
00:08:50.625 --> 00:08:54.541
you're usually not here on your birthday.
so I'm just surprised to see you.

174
00:08:54.625 --> 00:08:56.000
-Oh?
-I thought I wouldn't see you.

175
00:08:56.083 --> 00:08:58.083
-Apparently there's a surprise upstairs.
-Uh…

176
00:08:58.916 --> 00:09:01.125
The surprise is me
wishing you a happy birthday.

177
00:09:01.208 --> 00:09:02.958
Come on. my love.

178
00:09:03.041 --> 00:09:06.541
-Hmm.
-Oh. oh. Freedom. please go to the car.

179
00:09:06.625 --> 00:09:07.833
There's some money there.

180
00:09:08.750 --> 00:09:11.041
Please get a nice surprise for Jonasi.

181
00:09:11.125 --> 00:09:13.416
-And call Sarah. okay?
-Okay.

182
00:09:13.500 --> 00:09:16.291
-Would you like some food?
-Yes?

183
00:09:16.375 --> 00:09:18.166
-Food? Let's go upstairs.
-Ah.

184
00:09:22.375 --> 00:09:24.916
