-Okay.

185
00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:27.166
Come here. There we go.

186
00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:35.666
-What's wrong? Hmm?
-Oh! Uh-uh.

187
00:09:45.208 --> 00:09:46.416
