-Yes.

241
00:12:27.125 --> 00:12:28.125
What are we doing now?

242
00:12:28.208 --> 00:12:29.208
We're taking pictures.

243
00:12:29.291 --> 00:12:30.666
-Mmm.
-Goodness.

244
00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:32.916
-All right. sure.
-Take the picture.

245
00:12:39.458 --> 00:12:42.166
Let's see them. I don't trust him.

246
00:12:45.041 --> 00:12:47.375
-Wow.
-They're gorgeous.

247
00:12:47.458 --> 00:12:52.333
Whatever you do. please don't post
those pictures on social media.

248
00:12:54.208 --> 00:12:57.041
Uh. don't worry. Dad. I won't post them.

249
00:12:57.125 --> 00:12:58.833
That's my girl.

250
00:12:58.916 --> 00:13:01.291
-Freedom. take the knife and cut the cake.
-Let's have some cake.

251
00:13:01.375 --> 00:13:04.375
-Here we go.
-Here we go. Ah.

252
00:13:04.458 --> 00:13:06.083
Take the-- Goodness!

